snippet.textDisplay: What a collaboration!!!! This is a treat for every Allu Arjun fan.... Plus, perhaps this is the first multi-lingual song featuring Allu Arjun, and his first Hindi song as well (I'm not considering the dubbed versions)... The combination of Allu Arjun and Armaan Malik again created magic, and the participation of tri.be made this song more special. It took this song to international levels..... It is also perhaps the first Indo-Korean  collaboration in terms of music... Ye gaana to fire hai!!! 🔥🔥🔥.... Rukega nahi saala!!!! 🔥🔥🔥Thaggedele!!! 🔥🔥🔥
